import Mathlib

open Filter Set TopologicalSpace
open scoped Topology

theorem autoformalized_theorem_1259
  (X : Type*) [TopologicalSpace X]
  (hX : NormalSpace X)
  (s t : Set X)
  (hst : Disjoint s t)
  (hsk : IsClosed s)
  (h tk : IsClosed t) :
  ∃ U V, Disjoint U V ∧ closure U = s ∧ closure V = t := by sorry
